===Adjective===
{{en-adj|sorri|er}}

#Possessing [[sorrow]] or [[regret]].
#:''I am '''sorry''' I stepped on your toe.  It was an accident.''
#Poor, [[sad]] or [[regrettable]].
#:''The storm left his garden in a '''sorry''' state.''

